rtve-dl
Copyright 2026 Contributors

This product includes RTVE link resolution logic inspired by the Descargavideos project:
- forestrf/Descargavideos (not affiliated with RTVE)

In particular, the approach for extracting media URLs from RTVE "thumbnail" PNG metadata
and related heuristics were derived from Descargavideos' RTVE handler
(see their file `secundario/rtve.php` at the time this project was created).

This project does not include any DRM circumvention code. If RTVE marks an asset as DRM-protected,
rtve-dl will fail the run by default.

